(12, 1, 'p11', 'Which TWO of the following islands are known as ‘Crown dependencies’?', 'checkbox', 'There are also several islands which are closely linked with the UK but are not part of it: the Channel Islands and the Isle of Man. These have their own governments and are called ‘Crown dependencies’.', '2025-08-02 08:38:43'),
