(327, 14, 'p14', 'What is the name of the centrepiece to the Remembrance Day service located in Whitehall (London)?', 'radio', 'TheCenotaphin Whitehall is the site of the annual Remembrance Day service attended by the King, politicians and foreign ambassadors.', '2025-08-02 08:38:43'),
(328, 14, 'p15', 'What is the minimum age requirement in the UK for people to be able to drink wine or beer with a meal in a hotel or restaurant as long as they are with someone over 18?', 'radio', 'When they are16, people can drink wine or beer with a meal in a hotel or restaurant (including eating areas in pubs) as long as they are with someone over 18.', '2025-08-02 08:38:43'),
