(364, 16, 'p3', 'Which British athlete won 16 medals, including 11 gold medals, in races over five Paralympic Games?', 'radio', 'Baroness Tanni Grey-Thompson(1969-) is an athlete who uses a wheelchair and won 16 Paralympic medals, including 11 gold medals, in races over five Paralympic Games. She won the London Marathon six times and broke a total of 30 world records.', '2025-08-02 08:38:43'),
