(396, 17, 'p11', 'Who was the first person to sail single-handed around the world without stopping?', 'radio', 'A British sailor, Sir Francis Chichester, was the first person to sail singlehanded around the world, in 1966/67. Two years later,Sir Robin Knox-Johnstonbecame the first person to do this without stopping.', '2025-08-02 08:38:43'),
