(1820, 76, 'p19', 'Where are the Crown Jewels kept?', 'radio', 'The Crown Jewels are kept atthe Tower of London.', '2025-08-02 08:38:45'),
(1821, 76, 'p20', 'Which sport can be traced back to the 15th century in Scotland?', 'radio', 'The modern game ofgolfcan be traced back to 15th century Scotland.', '2025-08-02 08:38:45'),
