(1839, 77, 'p14', 'Lake District is the largest national park of England.', 'radio', 'This statement istrue.', '2025-08-02 08:38:45'),
(1840, 77, 'p15', 'What is the name of the area in London where famous theatres are located?', 'radio', 'London’s west end, also known as‘Theatreland’, is particularly well known for its theatres.', '2025-08-02 08:38:45'),
(1841, 77, 'p16', 'Which two of the following are key roles of school governors?', 'checkbox', 'Governors and school boards have an important part to play in raising school standards. They have three key roles:setting the strategic direction of the school, ensuring accountability andmonitoring and evaluating school performance.', '2025-08-02 08:38:45'),
(1842, 77, 'p17', 'What led the American colonies to want their independence from Britain?', 'radio', 'The British government wanted to tax the colonies.', '2025-08-02 08:38:45'),
