(1984, 83, 'p15', 'During the Middle Ages, who were the serfs?', 'radio', 'Serfs werepeasants who had a small area of their lord’s land where they could grow food.', '2025-08-02 08:38:45'),
(1985, 83, 'p16', 'Which invention lead to the rapid development of the industry in Britain during the 18th and 19th centuries?', 'radio', 'The Industrial Revolution was the rapid development of industry in Britain in the 18th and 19th centuries. Britain was the first country to industrialise on a large scale. It happened because of the development of machinery and the use ofsteam power.', '2025-08-02 08:38:45'),
(1986, 83, 'p17', 'MPs can only be contacted by post.', 'radio', 'False. You can contact MPs byletter or telephoneat their constituency office, or at their office in the House of Commons. In addition, many MPs, Assembly members, MSPs and MEPs hold regular local ‘surgeries’, where constituents can go in person to talk about issues that are of concern to them.', '2025-08-02 08:38:45'),
